author: @RasaAkstiniene
text:
LYRICS 
Intro: Wonwoo]
This is a story about us
On a day when the white snow was falling

[Verse 1: Joshua]
In the time passing over the snow
It seems like you painfully endured
The bitter sadness that was overflowing
(Ah-ah-ah)

[Pre-Chorus: Mingyu, Seungkwan]
I did too, just like you
Your sorrowful voice
When I hear it, I'll reach out my hand
Yeah-yeah-ayy

[Chorus: Jeonghan, Hoshi]
When the cold winter passes
We'll come to know
Even in the cold
The warmth of our blooming hearts is what protected us

[Post-Chorus: Vernon]
Stacking up our cherished hearts
It's the power of love
[Verse 2: S.Coups, The8, DK]
Words can sometimes be as sharp as a knifĞµ
So be careful with them
WhĞµn a sad voice reaches our ears
Let's reach out our hands right away
Let's show them our warmth

[Chorus: Hoshi, Woozi]
When the cold winter passes
We'll come to know
Even in the cold
The warmth of our blooming hearts is what protected us

[Post-Chorus: Jun]
Stacking up our cherished hearts
It's the power of love

[Bridge: DK, Seungkwan]
It's scary to take a step in this world but it's okay
At that time let's hold hands
Because we are together, we can meet a shining tomorrow

[Chorus: Wonwoo, Dino]
When the seasons come again
We'll come to know
In the Spring wind
What greeted us with a blooming heart and smile
[Post-Chorus: Jeonghan]
Stacking up our cherished hearts
It's the power of love

Source:
